1. SettingFontColor Example:

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>HTML Fonts Application</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <font face="Calibri" size="4">Hello YouTubers!</font><br />
        <font face="PWPerspective" size="4">Hello YouTubers!</font><br />
        <font face="Stencil Std" size="4">Hello YouTubers!</font>
    </body>
</html>

2. SetFontSize Example:

<body>
        <h3>HTML Fonts Application</h3>
        <font size="1">Hello YouTubers!</font><br />
        <font size="2">Hello YouTubers!</font><br />
        <font size="3">Hello YouTubers!</font><br />
        <font size="4">Hello YouTubers!</font><br />
        <font size="5">Hello YouTubers!</font><br />
        <font size="6">Hello YouTubers!</font>
    </body>

3. RelativeFontSize Example:

    <body>
        <h3>HTML Fonts Application</h3>
        <font size="-1">Hello YouTubers!</font><br />
        <font size="+1">Hello YouTubers!</font><br />
        <font size="-2">Hello YouTubers!</font><br />
        <font size="+2">Hello YouTubers!</font><br />
        <font size="-3">Hello YouTubers!</font><br />
        <font size="+3">Hello YouTubers!</font>
    </body>

4. SettingFontFace Example:

    <body>
        <font face="Calibri" size="4">Hello YouTubers!</font><br />
        <font face="PWPerspective" size="4">Hello YouTubers!</font><br />
        <font face="Stencil Std" size="4">Hello YouTubers!</font>
    </body>
